title.narrative: By 2022, the government has enhanced capacity and improved systems to implement inclusive and integrated social programmes and social protection

description.narrative: UNICEF has continued to stengthen government's social programmes, adjusting its support to the needs resulting from the COVID-19 pandemic. The MCCT programme guidelines were rapidly adjusted to ensure programme's continuity, and to prepare for an expansion. UNICEF also piloted digital birth registration and continued to support the implementation of disability registration / certification. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/07/2020
